{"tid":1474484,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[youtube 廢老channel] 洗頻集中帖，靠你地了","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:40:48.000Z","uid":21562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b15363a829edf7325b7858a41cf433eec166f885","tid":1474484,"uid":21562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"係我過往幾星期觀察番黎，好多廢老，絕大部分係話依家既後生仔搞亂社會，唔比佢地呢d年紀既人安享晚年（曾經聽過醫院靜坐都阻礙老人家去睇病啵），比我偷望到係搭輕鐵、坐公園同去酒樓飲茶既時候都會click入呢d廢老channel睇片，嘗試「了解」香港，就等同我地食飯冇屎痾既時候睇youtuber講下旅行、打機。呢d 廢老新一代揸住一部佢地唔識用既andriod 電話，又唔識裝app, 電話入面唯一既娛樂就係睇呢個本來已預設安裝既youtube, 而首當其衝就係一向充斥trending既普通話以及中國式煽動片段，而且對於佢地黎講已成為習慣，youtube亦都好貼心咁將呢一類影片不斷推薦比佢地，令佢地愈睇愈唔用腦，愈睇愈離地，再加上街坊圈子內一傳十，十傳百，「搞到香港亂」成為佢地既唯一「理據」。<br />\n<br />\n所以，由依家起，所有係連登既文宣同言論都要出現在以下youtube channel 的每一段片，並且將條片report。同一時間，係所有trending, 站係我地呢方既片，全部都入一入個video 刷觀看次數，抵消番我地因為要留言而送左比人既觀看人數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廢老channel 1: albert ip <a href=\"https://youtu.be/EygJQJUtT80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEygJQJUtT80&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=1d616dd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EygJQJUtT80</a><br />\n<br />\n廢老channel 2:厲害了中國 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM4FJofeZa_zQWdU9wsmdNg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCM4FJofeZa_zQWdU9wsmdNg&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=33a9466a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM4FJofeZa_zQWdU9wsmdNg</a><br />\n<br />\n廢老channel 3:快看資訊 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgkHTZsCdH8P9z7lazTXN3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCgkHTZsCdH8P9z7lazTXN3g&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=7cfefe9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgkHTZsCdH8P9z7lazTXN3g</a><br />\n<br />\n廢老channel 4:偉大復興 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClUsG4ddcYJIY695Tr9kjJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/li